dcterms:creator: A. Einstein
dcterms:description: A dataset representing the stochastic motion of a particle suspended in a fluid, characterized by a single parameter, the diffusion coefficient D.
dcterms:title: Brownian Motion (BM)

dcterms:creator: A. Sabri
X. Xu
D. Krapf
M. Weiss
dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of trajectories generated by fractional Brownian motion, characterized by correlated displacements and defined by the anomalous diffusion exponent α and the generalized diffusion coefficient D.
dcterms:title: Fractional Brownian Motion (FBM)

dcterms:creator: W. Wang
R. Metzler
A. G. Cherstvy
dcterms:description: A dataset representing scaled Brownian motion, which extends Brownian diffusion by considering an aging diffusion coefficient that scales with time, characterized by the anomalous diffusion exponent α and the constant D0.
dcterms:title: Scaled Brownian Motion (SBM)

dcterms:creator: G. Muñoz-Gil
B. Requena
G. Volpe
M. A. Garcia-March
C. Manzo
dcterms:description: A collection of datasets used for the AnDiChallenge, which includes various trajectories for training and validation in the context of anomalous diffusion.
dcterms:title: ANDI Datasets
